            "title": {
                "+content": "First impressions are the most lasting.",
                "+@gid": "2029378392",
                "+@lang": "EN"
            }
        },
        {
            "+@num": "2",
            "title": {
                "+content": "A man has free choice to begin love but not to end it.",
                "+@gid": "1980156912",
                "+@lang": "EN"
            }
        },
        {
            "+@num": "3",
            "title": {
                "+content": "In love there is both dotage and discretion.",
                "+@gid": "2987610267",
                "+@lang": "EN"
            }
        },
        {
            "+@num": "4",
            "title": {
                "+content": "Adversity makes a man wise.",
                "+@gid": "2752097213",
                "+@lang": "EN"
            }
        },
        {
            "+@num": "5",
            "title": {
                "+content": "Love is lawless.",
                "+@gid": "2346209809",
                "+@lang": "EN"
            }
        },
        {
            "+@num": "6",
            "title": {
                "+content": "Go to the sea, if you would fish well",
                "+@gid": "1546264683",
                "+@lang": "EN"
            }
        },
        {
            "+@num": "7",
            "title": {
                "+content": "Coming events cast their shadow before them.",
                "+@gid": "3273514092",
                "+@lang": "EN"
            }
        },
        {
            "+@num": "8",
            "title": {
                "+content": "Looks breed love.",
                "+@gid": "1860343973",
                "+@lang": "EN"
            }
        },
        {
            "+@num": "9",
            "title": {
                "+content": "The die is cast.",
                "+@gid": "2186379346",
                "+@lang": "EN"
            }
        },
        {
            "+@num": "10",
            "title": {
                "+content": "Absence makes the heart grow fonder.",
